WEBVTT

00:00:59.399 --> 00:00:59.799
What's wrong?

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:02.079
Nothing, I should go.

00:01:06.239 --> 00:01:06.640
Niannian.

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:09.680
You will definitely get better and better.

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:10.879
I wish you happiness.

00:01:20.079 --> 00:01:21.040
Cheers.

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:28.560
Why does the wine taste so good today?

00:01:30.239 --> 00:01:30.879
Niannian.

00:01:31.239 --> 00:01:32.599
I asked you out to dinner today...

00:01:32.599 --> 00:01:34.879
...because I wanted to announce some good news.

00:01:35.599 --> 00:01:38.239
Fang Qiu and I are officially together.

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:41.640
I can tell.

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:43.120
You are my best friend.

00:01:43.359 --> 00:01:44.319
Such a happy thing for me...

00:01:44.319 --> 00:01:45.879
...I definitely had to tell you first.

00:01:47.079 --> 00:01:48.079
Right, my dear?

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:50.799
Congratulations.

00:01:51.879 --> 00:01:52.560
Congratulations.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:53.640
Thank you.

00:01:54.159 --> 00:01:56.120
I think you treat me the best.

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.280
What, are you shy?

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:01.719
What's wrong with you?

00:02:01.719 --> 00:02:02.400
Um...

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:03.760
I...

00:02:03.959 --> 00:02:05.079
I have to go home today.

00:02:05.359 --> 00:02:06.200
My mom is waiting for me.

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.719
You just got here, aren't you going to eat something before you go?

00:02:08.639 --> 00:02:09.280
Niannian.

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:12.280
She went home.

00:02:12.759 --> 00:02:14.319
Why did you invite Niannian out?

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:16.719
She is my best friend.

00:02:17.479 --> 00:02:19.680
So, me falling in love is such a happy thing...

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:22.080
...it's only right that I tell her first.

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:24.719
Are you unhappy?

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:26.639
Or is it that...

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:28.479
...you like her?

00:02:28.719 --> 00:02:29.680
And didn't want her to know?

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:30.280
Di Fu.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:35.719
Eat by yourself.

00:02:36.479 --> 00:02:37.280
I have no appetite.

00:02:54.960 --> 00:02:56.919
Niannian, why are you here?

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.680
Why didn't you stay with Di Fu?

00:03:26.879 --> 00:03:27.400
Niannian.

00:03:27.879 --> 00:03:29.120
Actually, Di Fu and I...

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:29.840
Actually...

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.439
I think you two are a good match.

00:03:51.719 --> 00:03:53.400
It's late, I'll take you home.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.520
I'm not going home tonight.

00:03:58.879 --> 00:03:59.560
Why?

00:04:00.520 --> 00:04:01.319
Today I...

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:04.960
...came out because I fought with my mom.

00:04:06.479 --> 00:04:07.280
Originally...

00:04:09.039 --> 00:04:11.080
...I thought I'd stay at Di Fu's place.

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:13.120
But now...

00:04:14.280 --> 00:04:15.400
...I don't want to go there anymore.

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:16.319
Because I...

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:21.639
Right.

00:04:23.319 --> 00:04:24.120
Because of you.

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:27.959
I don't know why either.

00:04:27.959 --> 00:04:30.120
Suddenly it turned out like this.

00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:33.000
Thinking about it now...

00:04:36.120 --> 00:04:38.120
...she seems to have been like this since we were little.

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:41.480
As long as it's mine...

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:43.480
...she likes it.

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:47.319
As long as it's mine, she steals it.

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:51.360
But aren't we best friends?

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:54.879
I'm sorry.

00:04:57.560 --> 00:04:58.639
You don't need to apologize.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:01.279
Niannian.

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:03.519
It's too late now.

00:05:03.519 --> 00:05:04.560
It's unsafe outside.

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:06.480
How about this?

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.360
I'll find a nice hotel...

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:10.079
...and take you there for the night.

00:05:13.879 --> 00:05:14.680
Let's go to your place.

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:26.839
Do you know?

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:30.079
Actually, today is my birthday.

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:32.240
Then...

00:05:33.879 --> 00:05:34.839
...happy birthday.

00:05:39.560 --> 00:05:42.480
To- Today you sleep here.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:44.560
I- I'll go out first.

00:05:52.680 --> 00:05:55.120
You- You rest early.

00:06:16.399 --> 00:06:16.959
Di Fu.

00:06:17.839 --> 00:06:18.759
Why are you here?

00:06:18.759 --> 00:06:20.439
Di- Di Fu.

00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:25.680
Didn't I tell you not to betray me?

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.879
Did you think I couldn't do anything to you?

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:29.160
Di Fu, listen to me, it's not...

00:06:29.160 --> 00:06:30.120
Look at you.

00:06:31.279 --> 00:06:32.519
On one side is my good sister...

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:35.040
...and you turn around and steal my man.

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:38.279
You're the one who likes stealing men, right?

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:39.879
No father, no mother, no upbringing.

00:06:39.879 --> 00:06:41.240
So you just love stealing from others.

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.319
Are you sick?

00:06:43.439 --> 00:06:44.720
You're the one who's sick!

00:06:46.079 --> 00:06:46.680
Stop fighting!

00:06:48.759 --> 00:06:49.480
Fine.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:57.480
You recognize what this is, right?

00:06:58.399 --> 00:06:59.000
Lin Niannian.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.800
You know how many fans I have online, right?

00:07:02.079 --> 00:07:02.519
Let me tell you.

00:07:02.519 --> 00:07:03.680
Starting tomorrow,

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:05.839
I will make you the internet's

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:08.639
whore and the other woman.

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:10.319
Fang Qiu!

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:13.240
Do you really take me for a fool?

00:07:14.839 --> 00:07:16.560
I want the truth. Speak up!

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:17.759
If you don't speak, I'll kill you!

00:07:17.759 --> 00:07:19.240
No, no, no! Auntie, don't kill me!

00:07:19.240 --> 00:07:21.439
It was Di Fu! Di Fu killed Lin Niannian!

00:07:21.439 --> 00:07:22.480
It really has nothing to do with me!

00:07:22.480 --> 00:07:24.759
Auntie, really! Really!

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:29.279
Niannian is really dead.

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.360
I'm going to kill you!

00:07:34.360 --> 00:07:35.160
Ma Shan! Ma Shan!

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:35.959
You can't kill him.

00:07:36.399 --> 00:07:36.720
If you kill him,

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:38.120
you will never find your daughter.

00:07:43.839 --> 00:07:45.079
Lawyer Luo asked about it.

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:46.480
The road is passable tonight.

00:07:47.240 --> 00:07:48.079
I can't wait any longer.

00:07:48.079 --> 00:07:48.879
Call me if anything happens.

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:50.160
Also,

00:07:50.399 --> 00:07:51.920
if I'm not back by tomorrow morning,

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:52.800
call the police.

00:07:54.959 --> 00:07:55.720
I am a police officer.

00:07:56.959 --> 00:07:58.000
I can help you.

00:07:58.000 --> 00:08:00.279
My daughter has already been killed.

00:08:00.279 --> 00:08:02.079
Even if she's dead, we must find the body.

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:03.680
Only then can we follow the clues,

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:05.279
and punish the murderer.

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:06.040
Right?

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:07.959
Auntie Ma, Inspector Qi is right.

00:08:07.959 --> 00:08:08.920
Niannian is just missing.

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.120
She must be fine.

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:12.480
Do you know about the mother-daughter bond?

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:14.920
But what you are doing now is a crime.

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:17.040
If your daughter is still alive,

00:08:17.920 --> 00:08:19.839
wouldn't you be ruining yourself?

00:08:21.879 --> 00:08:22.879
Do you want to tell me,

00:08:24.079 --> 00:08:27.519
what exactly happened before your daughter lost contact?

00:08:30.920 --> 00:08:34.559
At that time, she said she didn't want to study anymore.

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:37.279
She wanted to livestream and be an influencer.

00:08:37.679 --> 00:08:38.200
Auntie.

00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:39.639
She also brought Di Fu...

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:41.480
Li Ren.

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:43.159
She brought Li Ren back home.

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:44.320
Haven't seen you in years.

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:45.120
Yes.

00:08:46.279 --> 00:08:47.960
You've become more and more beautiful.

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:48.840
Thank you, Auntie.

00:08:49.480 --> 00:08:50.080
Come, sit.

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:52.440
Come, come, just in time for dinner.

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:54.679
Mom, let me tell you.

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:55.879
Li Ren is now...

00:08:55.879 --> 00:08:57.159
she's a big influencer.

00:08:57.360 --> 00:08:58.919
She has millions of fans.

00:08:59.159 --> 00:09:01.879
She makes over a hundred thousand a month just from ads.

00:09:02.759 --> 00:09:03.120
By the way,

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:04.759
you've changed your name to Di Fu now.

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:06.200
From now on,

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:07.600
we have to call her Di Fu.

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:09.279
Di Fu.

00:09:09.840 --> 00:09:12.480
Just posting photos and videos online...

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:14.240
makes that much money?

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:15.679
Mom.

00:09:16.039 --> 00:09:17.480
It's not as simple as you think.

00:09:17.759 --> 00:09:18.519
You don't understand anything.

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:20.440
Auntie, let me explain. I...

00:09:23.720 --> 00:09:24.240
Sorry, Auntie.

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:24.960
I need to take this call.

00:09:25.159 --> 00:09:25.759
Go ahead.

00:09:31.519 --> 00:09:32.120
Hello?

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:35.840
A primer ad?

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.159
I can take it.

00:09:39.440 --> 00:09:40.360
My schedule is...

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:42.559
an eight-hour workday.

00:09:44.759 --> 00:09:45.759
Three thousand US dollars a day.

00:09:47.759 --> 00:09:49.679
Three thousand US dollars... a day?

00:09:49.679 --> 00:09:50.799
Overtime? I can't do overtime.

00:09:50.799 --> 00:09:51.720
Eight hours.

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:52.720
Okay.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:54.559
Let me think about it and call you back.

00:09:54.799 --> 00:09:55.279
Thanks.

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:56.879
See, didn't I say it makes money?

00:10:00.679 --> 00:10:02.120
I... let me explain to you.

00:10:02.399 --> 00:10:03.519
My job is...

00:10:12.879 --> 00:10:13.919
That way,

00:10:13.919 --> 00:10:15.559
the manufacturers naturally make money.

00:10:15.559 --> 00:10:17.240
Right, that's exactly how it works.

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:18.679
So I've decided,

00:10:18.919 --> 00:10:20.879
I want to do this too, just like Di Fu.

00:10:21.720 --> 00:10:23.000
Auntie, let me tell you,

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.279
Niannian is really smart.

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:25.799
If she works with me,

00:10:25.799 --> 00:10:27.279
she'll surpass me in no time.

00:10:27.519 --> 00:10:28.360
Really?

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:28.919
Really.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:32.159
I know you won't listen to whatever I say anyway.

00:10:32.639 --> 00:10:34.120
Fine, do it if you want.

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:36.559
Mom, you're the best!

00:10:36.759 --> 00:10:38.480
Yes! My mom agreed.

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:40.080
I told you Auntie would agree.

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:40.799
Di Fu.

00:10:41.039 --> 00:10:41.600
Thank you, Auntie.

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:44.639
You and Nana are like sisters.

00:10:44.960 --> 00:10:46.639
Consider yourself my second daughter.

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:47.919
Come home for dinner often.

00:10:47.919 --> 00:10:48.559
Auntie...

00:10:49.440 --> 00:10:50.879
I haven't had a mom since I was little.

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:53.120
Can I take you as my adoptive mother?

00:10:53.120 --> 00:10:53.759
Is that okay?

00:10:54.159 --> 00:10:54.759
Godmother.

00:10:55.399 --> 00:10:56.240
Yes, of course.

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:59.759
Then you can call me Godmother from now on.

00:11:00.159 --> 00:11:00.799
Godmother.

00:11:02.799 --> 00:11:03.840
Since then,

00:11:04.360 --> 00:11:06.440
Di Fu often came to my house to visit me.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:07.720
Bringing Niannian along,

00:11:07.720 --> 00:11:08.879
If you like Niannian,

00:11:09.159 --> 00:11:10.879
give Niannian a follow.

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:12.639
Niannian was very smart.

00:11:12.919 --> 00:11:14.320
She learned everything quickly.

00:11:15.399 --> 00:11:16.440
Before long,

00:11:17.159 --> 00:11:18.879
she became an influencer.

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:22.080
She soon made a lot of money.

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:25.120
Look, see if it looks good on you.

00:11:29.879 --> 00:11:30.519
It looks good.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:34.639
Our lives gradually got better, too.

00:11:36.679 --> 00:11:38.240
Perhaps seeing the money

00:11:39.399 --> 00:11:41.159
made me lower my guard.

00:11:42.960 --> 00:11:45.679
Until that red sports car appeared.